Hansen Transmissions Agrees to Cash-Offer Purchase by ZF Friedrichshafen

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-07-25T06:21:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/hansen-transmissions-agrees-to-cash-offer-purchase-by-zf-friedrichshafen.html
Hansen Transmissions International
NV (HSN)  said it agreed a cash offer with ZF Friedrichshafen AG where
ZF would acquire Hansen for 66 pence per share, or about 444.8
million pounds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  